==English==
===Alternative spellings===
*'''Ft'''

==={{Abbreviation}}===
'''Ft.'''

# [[fort|Fort]].
#:''Ft. Lauderdale''

====Usage notes====
As this abbreviation only eliminates the use of one character, the full word, [[Fort]], is generally preferred.  It is also never appropriate to use this abbreviation in body text in any form.  The same applies to [[Mt.]] for [[Mount]], [[So.]] for [[South]], and [[No.]] for [[North]]. Use of ''Ft.'' is only appropriate when space necessitates.